docs.text: About Me I am a computer science undergraduate at IIITH, currently (2024, fifth-year of my dual degree program) working on adiabatic quantum computing advised by Prof Shantanav Chakraborty and Prof Indranil Chakrabarty. Also, I often go by my nickname Arjo and can be found playing poker when bored.
